{"id":286343,"type":2,"name":"卡徒","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/da/18/286343_pjP33.jpg","summary":"数百年前，一场突如其来的陨石群撞击，让整个世界崩塌成两片彼此共生又绝对隔离的大陆。为了拯救危在旦夕的人类文明，数百位以罗森博格为首的原大陆科学家，集诸国之力研发出一种新型能源供给装置（卡片）。主人公陈暮从一个弱小无助、贫苦无依的困顿少年，在经历了一连串充满挣扎与磨难的冒险之后，没有放弃与退缩，依然靠着善良包容的天性、自身的卓绝努力与周围亲朋好友的热情相助，最终突破重重障碍，成长为一个正义凛然、以德服人、能力出众的正面领袖的故事。","info":"<li><span>话数: </span>13</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>2020年</li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/32644\">天工艺彩</a></li><li><span>原作: </span>方想</li>","collection":{"wish":6,"collect":2,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"中国","count":1},{"name":"网文改","count":1},{"name":"期待","count":1},{"name":"玄幻","count":1},{"name":"国产","count":1},{"name":"3D","count":1},{"name":"TV","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":895810,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/895810","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":895811,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/895811","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":895812,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/895812","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":895813,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/895813","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":895814,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/895814","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":895815,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/895815","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":895816,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/895816","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":895817,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/895817","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2099","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":895818,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/895818","type":